Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.14,0:10:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,¡Voy a correrme por el enorme\Ndel conserje frente a Aida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,¡Me vengo!
